title: SPY HAPPY HOUR OCTOBER 10TH 2014 w/ MMX & CHOCOLATL
description: SPY CEO and President Michael Marckx examines the pareto principle and shows how it applies to the SPY marketplace. Diana Moore of CHOCOLATL familiarizes SPY employees the methods the company takes to cultivate their cacao beans and shares the company's mission goals.
